    "Follow-up times of the implemented interventions were short, with only two studies conducting follow-up surveys at either 1 month post-intervention or 3 months postintervention completion.",
    "All other studies conducted follow-up surveys on intervention completion only.",
    "Due to impact bias, the duration of improvement may be overestimated.",
    "Surgical trainees are at risk of burnout, and it is a faculty responsibility to look after their trainee's well-being during training.",
    "This review highlighted that trainees of all genders and training level are unfortunately subject to harassment and increasing prevalence of burnout."
